verbose_text: To determine the effects of Tec on primary cultured articular chondrocytes, the chondrocytes were pre-incubated with Tec for 1 h, then stimulated with IL-1beta for 24 h. IL-1beta-stimulated chondrocytes exhibited upregulation of Col10a1, Cox-2, MMP-3 and MMP-13 levels, but downregulation of Runx1, Col2a1 and Acan expression levels (XREF_FIG C, # #P < 0.01, # # #P < 0.001).
